SOC Analyst Levels
Level 1 (L1)
Monitor alerts.
Perform initial investigations.
Escalate complex incidents.

Level 2 (L2)
Conduct deeper investigations.
Analyze malware and advanced threats.
Coordinate incident response activities.

Level 3 (L3)
Handle advanced threat hunting.
Develop detection rules.
Lead major incident investigations.

